      case 'soft-amber':     return { css:'linear-gradient(270deg,#f8f0e4 0%,#e0cca0 25%,#f0e8d8 50%,#d8c498 75%,#f8f0e4 100%)', dur:44 };
      default: return null;
    }
  }


  // ══════════════════════════════════════
  //  APPLY BACKGROUND + PALETTE
  // ══════════════════════════════════════
  function applyBackgroundSettings(settings) {
    if (!settings) return;

    if (settings.type === 'color') {
      body.classList.add('no-bg-animation');
      body.style.background = settings.value;
      body.style.backgroundSize = '';
      body.style.animation = 'none';
      colorPicker.value = settings.value;
      // Detect palette from the picked color
      applyPalette(detectPaletteFromColor(settings.value));

    } else if (settings.type === 'image') {
      body.classList.add('no-bg-animation');
      body.style.background = `url('${settings.value}') center/cover fixed no-repeat`;
      body.style.backgroundSize = 'cover';
      body.style.animation = 'none';
      // Sample image and apply matching palette
      detectPaletteFromImage(settings.value, function(pal) {
        applyPalette(pal);
      });

    } else if (settings.type === 'gradient') {
      const def = getGradientDef(settings.value);
      if (!def) return;
      body.classList.remove('no-bg-animation');
      body.style.background = def.css;
      body.style.backgroundSize = '600% 600%';
      body.style.animation = `bgShift ${def.dur}s ease infinite`;
      gradientPicker.value = settings.value;
      applyPalette(GRADIENT_PALETTE_MAP[settings.value] || P.purple);
    }
  }

  function reloadSavedOrStaged() { applyBackgroundSettings(getSaved() || staged); }
  function getSaved() { try { const r = localStorage.getItem(STORAGE_KEY); return r ? JSON.parse(r) : null; } catch(e) { return null; } }


  // ══════════════════════════════════════
  //  UI EVENT HANDLERS
  // ══════════════════════════════════════
  btn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    e.stopPropagation();
    const open = modal.style.display !== 'none';
    modal.style.display = open ? 'none' : 'block';
    if (!open) { btn.style.boxShadow = "0 0 10px var(--accent)"; btn.style.background = "var(--bg-hover)"; btn.style.borderColor = "var(--accent-bright)"; }
    else { btn.style.boxShadow = "none"; btn.style.background = "var(--bg-panel)"; btn.style.borderColor = "var(--accent)"; }
  });

  const closePanel = () => { modal.style.display = 'none'; btn.style.boxShadow = "none"; btn.style.background = "var(--bg-panel)"; btn.style.borderColor = "var(--accent)"; };
  closeBtn.addEventListener('click', closePanel);
  document.addEventListener('click', (e) => { if (modal.style.display === 'block' && !modal.contains(e.target) && e.target !== btn && !btn.contains(e.target)) closePanel(); });

  presetThumbs.forEach(img => {
    img.addEventListener('click', () => { staged = { type:'image', value:img.dataset.url }; presetThumbs.forEach(x => x.style.border = '1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2)'); img.style.border = '2px solid var(--accent)'; });
    img.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => { body.classList.add('no-bg-animation'); body.style.background = `url('${img.dataset.url}') center/cover fixed no-repeat`; });
    img.addEventListener('mouseleave', reloadSavedOrStaged);
  });

  colorPicker.addEventListener('input', () => { staged = { type:'color', value:colorPicker.value }; });
  colorPicker.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => { body.classList.add('no-bg-animation'); body.style.background = colorPicker.value; });
  colorPicker.addEventListener('mouseleave', reloadSavedOrStaged);
  gradientPicker.addEventListener('change', () => { staged = { type:'gradient', value:gradientPicker.value }; });

  uploadInput.addEventListener('change', e => {
    const f = e.target.files && e.target.files[0]; if (!f) return;
    const r = new FileReader();
    r.onload = () => { staged = { type:'image', value:r.result }; body.classList.add('no-bg-animation'); body.style.background = `url('${r.result}') center/cover fixed no-repeat`; };
    r.readAsDataURL(f);
  });

  applyBtn.addEventListener('click', () => { applyBackgroundSettings(staged); try { localStorage.setItem(STORAGE_KEY, JSON.stringify(staged)); } catch(e) {} closePanel(); });
  const saved = getSaved();
  applyBackgroundSettings(saved || staged);

})();
</script>



  
